== '''Itihas''' ==
Wadi ani Talaulim adim don veglle ganv asle, kiteak te vegllea komunidiche asle.1961 vorsa, Goenchea soddvonn zalea thoddea vorsam uprant, tancho karbhar ekuch ponchaiot korpak lagli. 

'Talaulim' mhonnche Konknnint  ‘ tin dongram ani eka nhoimche modlo zago’. Dusre vatten 'Wadi', ganvant xetkamti ani her ganvkar ravtat...'.

Donui ganvamni, Wadi ani Talaulim zaitinch devllam asat, jim Hindu devtank zoxe porim Narayan Dev, Hanuman, Ganpati, Krishna, Shree Bhutnath, Mahalaxmi ani Sateri Ladbai hankam orpon keleant, 

Choddxe Wadi-Talaulim ravpi os’sol Saxttichea ganvche  zoxe porim Lottle, Kolva, adi.    Talaulimchea sumarak 80% ravpeamchean aplim mullam fokot Kolvak dakhovnk zatat. Purtugezanche Goenche jikhe uprantchea survatechea kallant choddxe Saxttiche ( zo bhag Vhoddlea Kabizadacho aslo) lok dhormik chholl ani chodd promannant chol’lolea Kristanv korpantle vattavnk Talaulim stholantor zale. Wadi-Talaulim hantunt Kankonnchei ravpi asat je zaiteach karonnank lagun Vhoddlea Kabizada uprant usram aile.

